txt.en: Aslâ Khimash and his warband patrol the fields of Taur Drúadan, after having been sent from Cair Andros to assist in thwarting the Rohirrim's plans to ride south.
You have slain Aslâ Khimash and vanquished a threat to the safety of all that dwell within Far Anórien.
You have defeated Aslâ Khimash and his warband!

Aslâ Khimash can be found patrolling the northern fields of Taur Drúadan.\n\nYou have encountered Aslâ Khimash and should defeat the Easterling and his warband for the good of the people in Far Anórien.

Aslâ Khimash can be found patrolling the northern fields of Taur Drúadan.\n\nYou have encountered Aslâ Khimash and should defeat the Easterling and his warband for the good of the people in Far Anórien.

You have encountered Aslâ Khimash, the Easterling rider. He and his warband have been sent from Cair Andros to assist in thwarting the Rohirrim's plans to ride south. He and his allies must be defeated so the Rohirrim can continue their journey towards Minas Tirith.
